snippet.title: Travis Strikes Again: No More Heroes - Life is Destroy Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Stalk a serial killer through maze-like streets in the puzzle-action of Life is Destroy. Get into the game—literally—with Travis Strikes Again: No More Heroes, available January 18, 2019 on Nintendo Switch.

Learn more about Travis Strikes Again: No More Heroes for Nintendo Switch! https://goo.gl/PwwuYX
